com.hcl.domino.richtext.records

Interface RichTextRecord<T extends CDSignature>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the signature type of this record
    All Superinterfaces:
    MemoryStructure, ResizableMemoryStructure
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CDAction, CDActionBar, CDActionBarExt, CDActionByForm, CDBegin, CDBlobPart, CDCaption, CDDDEBegin, CDEnd, CDEvent, CDFileHeader, CDFileSegment, CDGraphic, CDHotspotBegin, CDHotspotEnd, CDImageHeader, CDImageHeader2, CDImageSegment, CDParagraph, CDText

    public interface RichTextRecord<T extends CDSignature>
extends ResizableMemoryStructure
    Base interface for rich text records. We provide sub interfaces for selected record types with extended functionality.

      Returns the length of the signature bytes containing the record type and total lengths at the beginning of getData()

      Returns the type of the record, if known.
